CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 24, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "At Fort Pitt Hotel - A panorama of fashions, to be held at the Fort Pitt Hotel, April 15, at 4 o'clock, sponsored by the Business and Professional Women's Club of the YWCA, has this group of women as committee members. Left to right: Jacqueline D. Gray, Ruth Smith, Louis L. Bullock, assistant program director for the East Area; Juanita McCarter, Dorothy Bobonis, Elizabeth Washington, Jeanne Brown and Laura W. Johnson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Business and Professional Women's Club of YWCA members: Jacqueline D. Gray, Ruth Smith, Louis L. Bullock, Juanita McCarter, Dorothy Bobonis, Elizabeth Washington, Jeanne Brown, and Laura W. Johnson, posed behind table in interior, another version
